openflap
by Alan Witkowski

https://github.com/jazztickets/openflap

Linux dependencies:
cmake
sdl2
sdl2-mixer
sdl2-image
sdl2-ttf

Building:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make -j`nproc`

Keys
Spacebar, mouseclick, or joystick button to jump.

Save data is in ~/.local/share/openflap

Set random number seed:
openflap [32-bit integer]